Backtesting metrics with Brazilian stocks
Sinc 30 Sep, 2014

Overview

A dynamic mix of long and short positions within the components of the Ibovespa in Brazil.

Configuração do Backtest

  1. Stock must be part of the Ibovespa index at the moment (t).
  2. Annual stock borrow fee rate of 3.5% applied for short position.
  3. SELIC RATE is used as a proxy of the national interest rate
